{"tid":613328,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加病到連比賽場刊都唔寫","createTime":"2018-04-01T15:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T08:22:55.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2411a9b64668b04be47da29a8e3f07c07efa8aac","tid":613328,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=1b63b5d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴周日對史篤城一戰賽前，球迷發現比賽場刊內的領隊專欄，由助理領隊保特代寫。<br />\n<br />\n當阿仙奴球迷看過周日對史篤城一戰前出版的場刊時，相信都會有疑問，事關平時由領隊雲加負責的領隊專欄，今次由助理領隊保特（Steve Bould）代寫，更引來廠迷在網上作熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n事實上雲加由於喉嚨痛而失聲，因此賽前的記者會都是由保特出席，而場刊內亦表明因由，但他們卻偏偏將場刊專欄一事，與雲加帥位問題扯上關係，有網民表示這是雲加很快被炒的先兆，另外亦有人認為保特將會是繼任人選，廠迷顯然將對雲加的不滿，透過互聯網發洩。<br />\n<br />\n事實上阿仙奴成績不如人意，要主帥雲加下台的聲音此起彼落。而這位老人家早前對此感不滿，向外表示這是外界對他的「年齡歧視」。"},{"pid":"0a8cd1c3d0fb96158503163f8f0160abf8c6eab8","tid":613328,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"yeah yeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081ca336afd83868414f6dede40234a418ac6f00","tid":613328,"uid":19012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"請珍惜重有雲加的日子"},{"pid":"3ec3a3971b36b48ea6e238560755d9909b71048e","tid":613328,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c53a53d1648689a4348ccd36c928ac965fcbc9","tid":613328,"uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:07:12.000Z","msg":"那段年月有多好　怎麼以後碰不到<br /